# Screenshots: the canonical screenshot-*.png files in assets/ are
# committed to the repo and updated by the Update Screenshots workflow
# (.github/workflows/screenshots.yml). They are NOT gitignored — doing
# so would make `git add assets/screenshot-*.png` in the workflow exit
# non-zero under `bash -e` (git refuses to add ignored paths), which is
# what historically caused the workflow to fail on every release tag.
#
# Only ignore the unnamed fallback artifacts produced by the raw
# filesystem extraction strategy in scripts/update-screenshots.sh; those
# are diagnostic-only and must never be committed.
assets/screenshot-unknown-*.png

# Claude Code
.claude/
